works.description: After the Audi R8-inspired catamaran designed by Bo Zolland and the Krassi Dimitrov’s Audi-inspired Y10 yacht, here comes the one that truly follows the German automaker’s brand values - progressive, sportive and premium. Audi has given Designboom an exclusive insight into the project. Developed by German designer Stephanie Behringer under the valued supervision of the Audi Concept Design in Munich, Germany, the luxury trimaran yacht has the Audi effect screaming from every nook and corner. The concept yacht combines two jet skis within a motorboat. The Audi trimaran yacht has its hull architecture based on a trimaran.
